# Pegasus Workflow Compatibility

This Cursor rule is secondary compatibility guidance. Prefer `.github/copilot-instructions.md`, `.github/agents/pegasus-orchestrator.agent.md`, `.github/instructions/`, and `AGENTS.md`.

The local coordinator loads `.github/references/orchestration/routing.md`; specialists load exact phase and result references. Active artifacts live under `docs/pegasus/changes/<change-id>/`; root phase files are templates.

Do not copy phase workflow, persistence, forecast, transport, or result contracts into Cursor rules. Missing local entry points, required references, authorization, or capability blocks before edits.
